'''Galactic News Network (GNN)''' was a large media corporation that reported on the events taking place in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] during the [[New Republic era]]<ref name="The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>. GNN's smaller bureaus would take local news stories and transmit them via courier [[Courier droid/Legends|newsdroids]] to the rest of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The company had an [[Indu GNN bureau|office]] on [[Indu San/Legends|Indu San]] that covered the [[Assassin/Legends|assassination]] of the [[Indu Council]]'s chief [[Councillor/Legends|councilor]], [[Shek Barayel]].

